name: TOPPERS ACE For MHT-CET 2025 (Maths) By Dinesh Sir
description:
THIS IS RECORDED COURSE OF MHT-CET (MATHS).
 
If you are aiming to score high percentile in MHT-CET 2025 Exam, then this is the best & perfect course for you to achieve the goal.

This Course having already Recorded Video of MHT-CET Full Syllabus.

About Course:	
This is MHT-CET Maths course which will cover full syllabus of Maths including 11th & 12th Class Chapters included in updated syllabus for MHT-CET 2025 Exam. Every Topic & Chapter will be covered with Basics & full Summary along with all formulas, concepts and various types of questions using various shortcut tricks for maximum topics. Maximum MCQ’s & PYQ’s based on various topics will be taught to enable students to solve any types of questions by themselves. This Course Consists of Full Syllabus Video Lectures of Previous Year Live course and not of this Year Live course.

Study Materials:	
Pdf Notes will be provided for each chapter with all the solution of MCQ’s.	
DPP based on each chapter will be available for maximum practice of students.	
Note:
Only Maths Subject carrying 100 Marks full syllabus (50% of MHT-CET Exam) will be available in this course.

*Rules for cancellation: After 5 days of Enrollment, only 50% amount will be refund. After 10 days, no refund. And within 5 days 500 Rs. + cancellation charges will Apply. Applicable for all courses. *

This book is created by Dinesh Sir & Team for MHT-CET 2024 (Maths) Aspirants.
